text: Abyshevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Romashkinskoye Rural Settlement of Alnashsky District, Udmurtia, Russia. The population was 28 as of 2008. There are 2 streets. == Geography == The village is located 6 km north-east from Alnashi and 81 km south-west from Izhevsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Udmurtia
title: Abyshevo, Udmurtia
